Protocol Design:
Leave room for crypto and authentication 
Make sure all sensitive fields are protectable
Make authentical mutual (comm between two parties, both parties should auth each other)

Digital certificates can be used for Identity management.

Routing Control mechanisms:
  admin can control which path is taken by the routers to send information between end users and outside the organization's network.










































































